'''RAR相关孤儿受体'''（{{lang-en|RAR-related orphan receptor}}，'''RORs'''）是[[核受体|核受体]]的一个家族，是[[细胞内|细胞内]][[转录因子|转录因子]]的一员<ref name="pmid7926749">{{cite journal | author = Giguère V, Tini M, Flock G, Ong E, Evans RM, Otulakowski G | title = Isoform-specific amino-terminal domains dictate DNA-binding properties of ROR alpha, a novel family of orphan hormone nuclear receptors | journal = Genes Dev. | volume = 8 | issue = 5 | pages = 538–53 | year = 1994 | pmid = 7926749 | doi = 10.1101/gad.8.5.538 }}</ref><ref name="pmid7811290">{{cite journal | author = Hirose T, Smith RJ, Jetten AM | title = ROR gamma: the third member of ROR/RZR orphan receptor subfamily that is highly expressed in skeletal muscle | journal = Biochem. Biophys. Res. Commun. | volume = 205 | issue = 3 | pages = 1976–83 | year = 1994 | pmid = 7811290 | doi = 10.1006/bbrc.1994.2902 }}</ref>。有三个ROR家族成员：'''[[RAR相关孤儿受体-α|ROR-α]]'''、'''[[RAR相关孤儿受体-β|-β]]'''和'''[[RAR相关孤儿受体-γ|-γ]]'''分别由基因{{gene|RORA}}、{{gene|RORB}}、{{gene|RORC}}编码。RORs的不寻常之处在于它们是以单体形式结合到{{le|激素反应元件|hormone response element}}上的，而其它大部分[[核受体|核受体]]都是以二聚体形式发挥作用<ref name="pmid11550795">{{cite journal | author = Jetten AM, Kurebayashi S, Ueda E | title = Progress in Nucleic Acid Research and Molecular Biology Volume 69 | journal = Prog. Nucleic Acid Res. Mol. Biol. | volume = 69 | issue = | pages = 205–47 | year = 2001 | pmid = 11550795 | doi = 10.1016/S0079-6603(01)69048-2 | chapter = The ROR nuclear orphan receptor subfamily: Critical regulators of multiple biological processes | series = Progress in Nucleic Acid Research and Molecular Biology | isbn = 978-0-12-540069-5 }}</ref>。

==配体==
目前已有[[褪黑素|褪黑素]]是ROR-α内源性[[配体_(生物化学)|配体]]的报道，而[[CGP_52608|CGP 52608]]是其人工合成的配体<ref name="pmid7885826">{{cite journal | author = Wiesenberg I, Missbach M, Kahlen JP, Schräder M, Carlberg C | title = Transcriptional activation of the nuclear receptor RZR alpha by the pineal gland hormone melatonin and identification of CGP 52608 as a synthetic ligand | journal = Nucleic Acids Res. | volume = 23 | issue = 3 | pages = 327–33 | year = 1995 | pmid = 7885826 | doi = 10.1093/nar/23.3.327 | pmc = 306679 }}</ref>。另外，X-射线晶体衍射（{{PDB|1n83}}和{{PDB2|1s0x}}）数据表明胆固醇或胆固醇衍生物都可能是内源性配体<ref name="pmid12467577">{{cite journal | author = Kallen JA, Schlaeppi JM, Bitsch F, Geisse S, Geiser M, Delhon I, Fournier B | title = X-ray structure of the hRORalpha LBD at 1.63 A: structural and functional data that cholesterol or a cholesterol derivative is the natural ligand of RORalpha | journal = Structure | volume = 10 | issue = 12 | pages = 1697–707 | pmid = 12467577 | doi = 10.1016/S0969-2126(02)00912-7 | url = http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0969212602009127 | date = December 2002 | access-date = 2013-12-01 | archive-date = 2019-02-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190217162428/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0969212602009127 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

与之相反，全反式[[维A酸|维A酸]]对ROR-β和-γ有高亲和性，但对ROR-α全无<ref name="pmid12958591">{{cite journal | author = Stehlin-Gaon C, Willmann D, Zeyer D, Sanglier S, Van Dorsselaer A, Renaud JP, Moras D, Schüle R | title = All-trans retinoic acid is a ligand for the orphan nuclear receptor ROR beta | journal = Nat. Struct. Biol. | volume = 10 | issue = 10 | pages = 820–5 | year = 2003 | pmid = 12958591 | doi = 10.1038/nsb979 }}</ref>。

==功能==
三种RORs在各个系统中起一些重要角色作用<ref name="pmid15584888">{{cite journal | author = Jetten AM | title = Recent advances in the mechanisms of action and physiological functions of the retinoid-related orphan receptors (RORs) | journal = Current drug targets. Inflammation and allergy | volume = 3 | issue = 4 | pages = 395–412 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15584888 | doi = 10.2174/1568010042634497 | url = http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/ben/cdtia/2004/00000003/00000004/art00007 | access-date = 2013-12-01 | archive-date = 2013-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203015117/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/ben/cdtia/2004/00000003/00000004/art00007 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，包括：
* ROR-α - [[小脑|小脑]]和[[淋巴结|淋巴结]]的发育，{{le|脂质代谢|lipid metabolism}}，[[免疫反应|免疫反应]]，[[骨|骨]]维持
* ROR-β - 在大脑和视网膜的高度表达，但精确作用未知
* ROR-γ - 淋巴结发育，免疫反应，{{le|TH17辅助细胞|T helper 17 cell}}的存活

